Display &amp; Presentation Support: &apos;Projector/Display Setup &amp; Support&apos; (e.g., &apos;Can&apos;t connect to the projector,&apos; &apos;Conference room display issue&apos;).

General Break-Fix &amp; Support: &apos;Report Device Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;My laptop is slow,&apos; &apos;My computer won&apos;t turn on,&apos; &apos;My phone screen is cracked,&apos; &apos;My monitor is flickering,&apos; &apos;My dock isn&apos;t working&apos;).

